PREAMB.P:
Based on our analysis in this EA of the proposed action as specified in the license application, we conclude that licensing the project would be likely to adversely affect EFH for the UCR Chinook salmon for the same reasons we conclude that licensing the project would adversely affect the UCR steelhead and its designated critical habitats (see section 1.3.3, 
Endangered Species Act
). Consequently, we will request that NMFS provide any EFH recommendation along with its biological opinion regarding listed anadromous fish.

